Package org.letras.ps.region

Class Summary
AbstractRegionSet Abstract base class for RegionSets that provides change notification services to implementors.
DigitalInkDispatcher The DigitalInkDispatcher sends RegionSamples and RegionEvents to the channels of IRegions.
DigitalInkProcessor The DigitalInkProcessor is responsible for ordering and generating RegionEvents.
RegionManager The RegionManager owns the node's RegionTreeNode model.
RegionProcessor The RegionProcessor is the applications main entry point and is responsible for instantiating all relevant components that make up an instance of the RegionProcessingStage.
RegionSampleProcessor The RegionSampleProcessor contains a region model and dispatches samples to the applications that are registered on the model elements.
RegionSampleProcessorFactory An ISampleProcessorFactory that instantiates RegionSampleProcessors.
RegionSet A RegionSet is a container that allows batch publication of Regions.
RegionTreeNode A Region in the hierarchy.
RpConsole Provides a simple console UI to the raw data processor controlling a Mundo node providing the raw data processing stage in the pipeline.
